    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Photographs of an individual person, printed in the specific size required for inclusion into a passport. Often these are taken with cameras built for this purpose.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
